# LidoPro local development environment
#
# Optional Android Studio launcher override for Capacitor.
# The helper script also auto-detects common Linux install paths.
# CAPACITOR_ANDROID_STUDIO_PATH=/opt/android-studio/bin/studio.sh
#
# Optional Android live-reload host override.
# By default scripts/cap-android-dev.sh uses the Android Emulator host
# alias and points Capacitor to http://10.0.2.2:5173.
# For a physical tablet, set the host LAN IP explicitly.
# LIDOPRO_ANDROID_DEV_HOST=192.168.1.20
# LIDOPRO_DEV_SERVER_PORT=5173
# LIDOPRO_CAPACITOR_SERVER_URL=http://192.168.1.20:5173
#
# Optional Tauri/WebKitGTK overrides for local Linux desktop debugging.
# The helper script sets these automatically on Linux/Wayland when useful.
# WEBKIT_DISABLE_DMABUF_RENDERER=1
# GDK_BACKEND=x11
#
# Do not commit real credentials, API keys, payment provider secrets,
# customer data, production URLs, or deployment material.
